text:
Photo: Codi Mills, The Chronicle Police cars line the streets of a subdivision during a search for a shooting suspect on Serramonte Blvd. on March 8, 2014 in Daly City, Calif. Police cars line the streets of a subdivision during a search for a...
San Francisco Police detained four people Wednesday afternoon after a manhunt that started in Oakland crossed the bay, authorities said.
